living. Thebillalsorequiresthedepartmentofhealthandhumanservicestoobtainadetermination
of an applicant’s need for long term care from the applicant or participant’s primary care physician,
physician assistant, or advanced practice registered nurse, and to consider information from other
healthcareproviders.
